snippet.title: News 5 Cleveland
snippet.description: News 5 is the leading television station in Northeast Ohio. A proud affiliate of the ABC network, News 5 was the first television station in Ohio. Due to reports of widespread inappropriate links being shared on YouTube videos across our company, News 5 is temporarily disabling comments on videos, as of March 10, 2021.
